<C>__{bud}
<D>__{miss kubelik!}
<A>__{meanwhile fran has appeared from the bathroom, and is approaching the bedroom door. she is still in her robe, and is holding a double sock stretcher with one of bud's socks on it. bud, rounding the corner from the kitchen at full speed, collides with fran in the bedroom doorway. he grabs her arms with obvious relief.}
<C>__{bud}
<D>__{are you all right?}
<C>__{fran}
<D>__{sure.}
