<D>__{it's very curious i could only find three and a half pair.}
<C>__{bud}
<D>__{well, things are a little disorganized around here.}
<A>__{he carries the bag of groceries into the kitchen, fran trailing after him. during the following, he removes the contents of the bag bread, eggs, bacon, spaghetti, ground round, frankfurters, and assorted canned goods sets them out on the drainboard.}
