<D>__{i'd say. what's a tennis racquet doing in the kitchen?}
<A>__{she produces the racquet from behind the stove.}
<C>__{bud}
<D>__{tennis racquet? oh, i remember i was cooking myself an italian dinner.}
<P>__{(fran looks at him oddly)}
<D>__{i used it to strain the spaghetti.}
